            <abstract>
                <p>A collection of 90 <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/Qene">qǝne poems</ref> of different kinds: 
                    65 <foreign xml:lang="gez">śǝllāse</foreign>, 
                    twelve <foreign xml:lang="gez">mawaddǝs</foreign>, 
                    eight <foreign xml:lang="gez">wāzemā</foreign>,
                    four <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿǝṭāna mogar</foreign> 
                    and one <foreign xml:lang="gez">za-yǝʾǝze-ni</foreign>.</p>
